    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Follow the Robot FrameWork(RFW) Installation steps section in below wiki"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "RFW + UTF test dev environment - CT/ESC Software Home - Docupedia (bosch.com)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Make sure Cntlm runs in background when you execute Pip install command"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Install python 3.8 from this link https://www.python.org/downloads/release/python-380/"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "verify python by giving command python in command prompt"
      ]
    },
